git-hub: https://github.com/masthan55/all-setup.git

1. Create 3-servers. 1-main-server, 2-worker-node servers.                                                      [Node-exporter ---> prometheus ---> graphana dash-bord].
 * main server (all-script)                                // install "pegion.sh" script.
 * worker-1 (install node-exporter)  from git ()           // if you dont install node-exporter 
 * worker-2 (install node-exporter)

2. connect to prometheus main-server.
 * vim /etc/prometheus/prometheus.yml  
 * vim /etc/hosts
   5.25.658.657 worker-1          (copy public-ip of worker-1)
   3.54.548.552 worker-2          (copy public-ip of worker-2)   

3. go to prometheus refreash and check host(option).
  * if you can see worker-1 and worker-2 it's completed.
 
4. PROMETHERUS: 9090            // All port nbrs.
   NODE EXPORTER: 9100
   GRAFANA: 3000

5. CONNECTING PROMETHEUS TO GARAFANA:
   connect to grafana dashboard -- > Add your first "Data source" -- > add -- > promethus -- > url of prometheus -- > save & test -- >
   top of page -- > explore data -- > if you want run some queries -- > top -- > import dashboard -- > 1860 -- > laod --- > prometheus -- > import 
